window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Each of Sean's wives takes a moment to share a tale of their past while sitting around having a drink. Contains the Valens Legacy novellas <i>Peg and Cali</i> and <i>Estrella and Other Stories</i>. </p> <p><b><i>Peg and Cali </i></b></p> <p>Peg tells of the events that led up to her and Sheila becoming close. Cali tells the tale of why she was chosen to become and assassin and a little about her training. </p> <p><b><i>Estrella and Other Stories </i></b></p> <p>Estrella tells of the events that led to her becoming trapped in the Onderwereld.</p> <p><b>Warning: Contains mature content.</b></p>"; 
